8-01-28T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"又就過年了<br />\n十周年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T09:44:36.000Z","msg":"時間過得好快.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年高登年代. <br />\n我阿媽重叫我開電腦比佢睇, 但唔好意思比佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最正係 越出越多相, 大家每日都等突發相出現. <br />\n奇拿 無睇漫畫都好少人知咩來. ....出晒名<br />\n<br />\n估唔到希哥 依家撈得好掂 , 之前重為女友出頭 鬧林志玲<br />\n好似重結咗婚. 又係果句 .. 公平咩. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d22623691333e61624be9ef44149fbf45e4c36","tid":543611,"uid":138420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T09:48:28.000Z","msg":"突然十年又過去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}